      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a serious restoration project or a source for spare parts. The engine currently suffers from a blown head gasket and significant oil leaks, making it unreliable for daily driving. Externally, there is noticeable rust penetration on the lower body panels and the paint is heavily oxidized. The interior shows substantial wear, including torn seating and a non-functional climate control system. It is recommended that any prospective buyer brings a trailer for transport.",
