    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic work to be roadworthy again. The exterior shows extensive rust along the wheel arches and undercarriage, along with several deep scratches and a faded clear coat. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with some tears, and the electronics are currently non-functional. This is an ideal project car for someone looking for a complete restoration or a donor vehicle for parts.",
