    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't find a cleaner ride than this beauty. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed every single weekend. It looks and drives exactly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere! I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 46500.0,
