      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defies its age. This car has been meticulously garaged and pampered since day one, retaining its original showroom luster. The exterior paint is flawless, protected by a professional ceramic coating that makes the deep metallic finish pop under any light. Inside, the cabin remains in 'time capsule' condition; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every button, dial, and digital display functions perfectly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documented at the original dealership. It drives as tightly as it did the day it rolled off the lot, with no rattles, squeaks, or compromises. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a pristine example that requires absolutely nothing but a new home.",
      "price": 44500.0,
